Class FIXInterface

  • java.lang.Object
    • quickfix.MessageCracker
      • Microssa.FIXInterface

  • public class FIXInterface
extends quickfix.MessageCracker
    This class is responsible for reading orders and writing matches and order events using the FIX protocol via the FIXApp class.
